\id 3JN - Maka NT [mca] -Paraguay (web 2014) 
\h 3 JUAN 
\toc1 3 JUAN 
\toc2 3 Juan 
\toc3 3Jn 
\mt1 3 JUAN 
\c 1  
\s1 Juan wenq'ika'ai pa' Gayo. 
\p  
\v 1 Yakha' witlijtsitjii tenek'enhe'yij hika' e'm ha'ne witfaakanek akha' Gayo. Yakha' qi in k'esu'un.\x * \xo 1:1 \xt 2Jn 1; Jn 14:6; 1Jn 5:20\x* 
\s1 Juan qi in yisu'un pa' Gayo. 
\p  
\v 2 Yejefe qi in k'esu'un, yakha' ewi'ƚƚe in k'iyinijets pa' Intata qu' ne'fenij week pa'qu' ƚunye'je' qu' aqsiijkii qa k'iyinijets iye qu' nafits in yijaa'ija in ƚijayan pa' Intata qu' ham aats'eye'.\x * \xo 1:2 \xt 1Ti 1:10\x* 
\v 3 Qi in tsi'sinheti'mkii in namyii he' uja'x inejefetsipji' pa' Intata qa nifel ye'mik'i pa' ejunye'j in yijaa'ija in ƚijayaanija pa' Intata.\x * \xo 1:3 \xt Jn 15:26; Hch 26:5; 2Jn 4\x* 
\v 4 Les qiijiija qa ƚe'wisji'ij ye'mkii qa k'impiye'ji'jij hekhewe' yijatshenhei in nite' yili'ij in yijayaanija ke' Intata ƚe'lijei.\x * \xo 1:4 \xt Jn 15:11; 1Co 4:14; Ga 4:19; Fil 2:22\x* 
\v 5 Yejefe qi in k'esu'un, yakha' hit'ij ewets in qi'ija in ƚe'wis ka' eqfenye'jij in ƚeneqjunu'uj qa ƚ'iftits'ets iye hekhewe' hats yijayan ha' Cristo. Qa qi'ija iye in ƚe'wis in ƚeneqjunuji'jij pekhewe' nite' ƚenikfeltaxij hats yijayan ha' Cristo.  
\v 6 Enewe'en in yamjii na'aj witset qa nifelji'ijkii pa' eqfenyejeiji'jij in qi'ija in ƚisu'un qa ƚeneqjunu'uj iye, i'njiijifi pe' witlitsitjii qa nifelji'ji'm pe' hats yijayan ha' Cristo. Qa k'iyinij ewets qu' i'fenij week pa'qu' hami'ik'ui qu' net'ejuyets qu' nakkii iye qu' nenfel ke' Intata ƚe'lijei qe hik aka' yisu'un pa' Intata hats'inha qa' ƚe'wiise'ƚe qu' nakkii iye,\x * \xo 1:6 \xt Mt 16:18; 1Co 10:31; 14:4; 16:6; Ap 1:4; Hch 15:3; 20:38; 21:5; Ro 15:24; 2Co 1:16; Tit 3:13; 1Ts 2:12\x* 
\v 7 qe ƚekhewel in ikkii ta'ƚets in t'ithayi'yi'm ha' Jesucristo qa nite' yisu'un qu' net'eku'miju'ƚ na'aj tistaxij pekhewe' nite' yijayan ha' Cristo.\x * \xo 1:7 \xt Jn 10:25; Hch 15:14; Ap 14:1; 1Co 9:15-18\x* 
\v 8 Qa hik ta'ƚijupi' inekhewel qu' jintaqsiijkiyek pe'ye' hats'inha qa' week ji'nt'ithayiyi'ƚ pekhewe'en. Ma' qa' hik ƚunye'je' qu' ewi'ƚ jina'niji' pa' i'nithayijkit in jitefel ke' Intata ƚe'lijei. 
\s1 Pa' Diótrefes uƚ'ax pa' ƚunye'j. 
\p  
\v 9 Yakha' in hika' ka' hayiits witfaakanek t'ejuitaxets hekhewe' hats yijayan ha' Cristo, qa hakha'ƚe Diótrefes qa nite' yisu'un qe ƚakha' yisu'untax qu' les qi qu' netnek'enhei qa nite' tsisu'untaxi'ƚ yekheweli'ƚ in heinek'enhe'yi'ƚij hekhewe' hats yijayan ha' Cristo.\x * \xo 1:9 \xt Mt 20:25-28; 23:5-12; Col 1:18; 1P 5:2-3; 2Jn 9; Hch 18:27; Ro 16:1-2; 2Co 3:1\x* 
\v 10 Qa hik ta'ƚijupi' qu' ƚeke'ye' qu' natsamii hatse' qa' week henfelji'ju' hekhewe' hats yijayan ha' Cristo ka' ƚunye'j ha' Diótrefes qi in uƚ'ax qa uƚ'etsik'i iye pe' ƚe'lijeyi'ƚ yiwetskii. Qa ekewe'en nite' uja'xƚe qu' naqsiijkii qe na'l iye kakhap iye yaqsiijkii kakha'an, in t'oqoweijiiju'ƚ hekhewe' inejefets in yamtaxii pa'aj ke' witlijtsitjii hik hekhewe' ikijfik'i qu' nenfel ke' Intata ƚe'lijei. Qa pe' neqjunutaxij ma' qa yiwu'mik'uifik'i ke' ƚe'lijtsitjii.\x * \xo 1:10 \xt 1Ti 5:13\x* 
\s1 Pa' Demetrio ƚe'wis pa' ƚunye'j. 
\p  
\v 11 Yejefe qi in k'esu'un, yakha' hit'ij ewets qu' hasu'uj eneqjeyu'uj qu' aqsiijkii pa' uƚ'ax. Eneqjeyu'uj yijat'ij qu' aqsiijkii pa' qi ƚe'wis. Pakha' qu' naqsiijkii pa' ƚe'wis pakha'an yatsat'axij pa' Intata. Qa pakha'ƚe qu' naqsiijkii pa' uƚ'ax pakha'an nite' nikfe'lets pa' Intata.\x * \xo 1:11 \xt 1P 3:17; 1Jn 4:4; Ex 33:20\x* 
\v 12 Week yit'ijets in ƚe'wis pa' yaqsiijkii ha' Demetrio. Qa week yit'ijets iye in yijaa'ija in yaqsiijkii pa' yit'ij ke' Intata ƚe'lijei. Qa yekheweli'ƚ iye hik aka' hit'iƚijju' iye. Qa akha' hats ƚenikfe'lets week na'aj hit'iƚijju' in yijaa'ija.\x * \xo 1:12 \xt 1Jn 2:20-21; Jn 21:24\x* 
\s1 Wetfel. 
\p  
\v 13 Olotstax ke' hisu'untax qu' henfel e'm qa nite'ƚe hisu'un qu' henji' ha'ne witfaakanek.  
\v 14 Q'ax qu' ƚeke'ye' hatse' qu' natsam ei qa' jintafaakateiju'ha.  
\v 15 Na'lƚek pa' Intata qu' neƚisij pa' wit'ikesimeya'x. Enewe' ejuwaikal wetfel ei. Qa akha' qu' enfeli'mek hekhewep yijuwaikali'ƚ in hewetfeli'ƚii. Qa hasu'uj pa' qu'nte' enfeli'im.